        B. T. Fan, A. Panaye, J. P. Doucet, and A. Barbu. "Ring Perception: A
        New Algorithm for Directly Finding the Smallest Set of Smallest Rings
        from a Connection Table." *J. Chem. Inf. Comput. Sci.* **33**,
        p. 657-662 (1993).
